data.description: Welcome to the heart of Tucker, GA! This lovely 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home is located not only at the center of new developments and plans but it is also nestled in the desirable Brockett Creek Estates. The lot is level and private with plenty of front and back yard space. The back yard has an attached deck, it is fenced and private, and is the perfect oasis to retreat and relax. There is an attached 2 car garage and plenty of additional on and off street parking. The entry foyer is inviting and the floorplan is both functional and spacious. The white kitchen has ample cabinet space, a breakfast bar, as well as an eat-in kitchen area. There is a living room with a cozy fireplace and there is also a full bedroom and bathroom on the main level. The primary bedroom is oversized and can even be converted into a secondary room. There is a bonus room on the upper level which would be ideal for a home office, craft room, or maybe a playroom. This home is move-in ready with newer windows, HVAC, and roof. The hot water heater also was just installed last year. This home is an empty canvas and ready for your finishing touches. Don't hesitate. Schedule your exclusive showing today.
